aircraft but he had no further information 
asmara is an important military air base as well as a pickup 
point for cargo planes ferrying relief food to ethiopian drought 
victims 
president mengistu haile mariams government rarely comments on 
claims of the separatist rebels who are waging wars in the 
provinces of tigre and eritrea there was no way to independently 
confirm the rebel report 
