childrens advocates on thursday announced a 
safe kids campaign designed to combat the leading killer of 
americas children injuries that can be prevented 
preventable injuries are epidemic in this country these 
things are preventable and thats what people have to be made aware 
of actress markie post of nbctvs night court said at a 
